string.name: content_privacy_chap1
string.value: Transparency  and  controllability ,  user benefits, legal compliance, and the data security are the basic principles  of  the Huawei's privacy protection. We integrate these principles into product design and transition to the whole process of product development.

string.name: content_privacy_chap2
string.value: We initially use the least amount of data  to provide you with the most convenient service. At the same time, you have the right to know and control your data and Huawei's processing of the data.
